<ul>
  <li>
    Step one: <u> Registration and login </u> <br>
    At first you have to register at coma and login. <br>
    Notice: You only need one account for all conferences you want to take part in. <br>
    <br>
  </li>
</ul>

<ul>
  <li>
    Step two: <u> Apply as an reviewer and log into a conference </u><br>
    At the conference of your choice press the button named 
    <a href="./help.php?for=conference+overview{&popup}{&SID}"> apply as reviewer </a> 
    to get the status of a reviewer. <br> Now log into the conference.<br>
    <br>
  </li>
</ul>

<ul>
  <li>
    Step three: <u> Specify your preferences und manage your reviews </u> <br>
    The item <a href="./help.php?for=reviewer_prefers{&popup}{&SID}"> Edit my preferences  
    </a> enables you to specify what topics you prefer. <br>
    You can download papers, which are assigned to you, and review them at the item 
    <a href="./help.php?for=reviewer_reviews{&popup}{&SID}"> Manage your reviews </a>. <br>
    You are able to discuss the paper in the forum with other reviewers of this paper.<br>
    Please pay attention to the "deadline for reviews". <br>
  </li>
</ul>
